com.inqwell.any

Class AnySet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.AbstractComposite
      • com.inqwell.any.AnySet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, Composite, Set, Serializable, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OrderedSet, SimpleSet

    public abstract class AnySet
extends AbstractComposite
implements Set, Cloneable
    A general collection class hashing Anys into a unique set. It is an abstract class providing an in-memory Set implementation acting as a basis for concrete imnplementations.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    Author:
    $Author: sanderst $
